name: Golden Club T-shirt
description:
High Roller Clothing was founded with the concept to make gambling a fashion statement. The brand takes inspiration from all your favorite casino games with a unique theme for every shirt. Our shirts take a modern approach to the high roller lifestyle in everyone. 

All Over Print. with discharged Ink. 4.5 oz., pre-shrunk 100% ringspun cotton, Double-needle stitched neckline and sleeves 1/4 turned, Shoulder-to-shoulder taping, 3/4" seamless collar 
Sizes M-2XL
